Overview

Demonstrates borrower processing when required documentation is missing during intake and process validation.

The recording validates missing document detection, document request generation, follow-up scheduling, governance updates, and operational handling of incomplete borrower applications.

Recording Objectives

Demonstrate:

Borrower intake

Missing document detection

Document request generation

Follow-up scheduling

Governance updates

Audit logging

Pending document disposition
Recording Scenario

Example:

Borrower Application

Income Documentation:
Missing

Expected Outcome:

Missing Docs Detected

Document Request Created

Follow-Up Scheduled

Pending Docs Status
